tweet: "If they come five years from now and say, 'Hey, I think that that wristwatch is mine,' we will still have that money from the auction for that property owner."  Currently, around 4,000 items are available in the two-day auction. @WNEP   https://t.co/GOcXlkoSKV

name: PA Treasurer Stacy Garrity
tweet: Happening TODAY (3/23) and tomorrow (3/24), my office is holding an online auction of unclaimed property to include items such as a one-ounce gold bar; a Rolex watch, and some South African Krugerrand gold coins.  https://t.co/MsLOzLTi1C

name: PA Treasurer Stacy Garrity
tweet: Thank you to @SenatorGORDNER for joining me yesterday on a tour of Treasury’s vault! It's always great getting the word out about the $4 billion in unclaimed property we are trying to get back to Pennsylvanians.  https://t.co/jbKEnAAr2d
